幾何平均 (GEOMEAN) 計算 
$$ GEOMEAN \ = \sqrt[5]{9 \times 7 \times 5 \times 7 \times 9} \ = 7.236527563504052
$$

驗算: $| 7.236527563504052^5-(9 \times 7 \times 5 \times 7 \times 9)| \ll 1$, 符合定義

方案選擇:
- 方案 B: 1 + floor(GEOMEAN)
- 1 + floor(7.236527563504052) = 1 + 7 = 8

自我評量總分: 8 / 10